Author: risaeola
Text: i had my initial appointment for treatment yesterday. it’s hard and it’s scary and it’s draining. this disorder fucks you up so much. i feel like part of me was expecting for them to say i’m fine and nothing is wrong with me. then she told me that i have a disorder and that i could really get myself in some trouble medically if i’m not careful and it was both a relief to have that validation but so scary at the same time. like, shit, i don’t want to die, i just want to be skinny.
